{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 🧠 LangGraph Memory 全面解析\n",
    "\n",
    "> 从「学概念」走向「做系统设计」的关键一步"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 一、这节课到底用了哪几种 Memory？\n",
    "\n",
    "本质上用了 **两类 memory（一个概念 + 两种 schema）**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1️⃣ Long-term Memory（长期记忆）\n",
    "\n",
    "这是这节课真正的重点。通过："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Long-term Memory 的核心操作\n",
    "# store.put(...)   # 存储\n",
    "# store.search(...) # 检索"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "特点：\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "跨 thread ✅\n",
    "跨对话 ✅\n",
    "长期存在 ✅\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "可以理解为：**一个外部数据库（Memory Store）**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2️⃣ Memory Schema（两种结构）\n",
    "\n",
    "这节课不是只讲"存 memory"，而是讲：**怎么结构化存 memory**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### (1) Profile Memory（用户画像）📋\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "User Profile\n",
    "- name\n",
    "- preferences\n",
    "- traits\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "例子：用户喜欢披萨、用户在加拿大\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 特点：\n",
    "- 结构化\n",
    "- 聚合型（一个用户一个 profile）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### (2) Collection Memory（事件集合）📝\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "Memory list\n",
    "- memory1\n",
    "- memory2\n",
    "- memory3\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "例子：喜欢披萨、喜欢猫、喜欢编程\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 特点：\n",
    "- append-only（不断增加）\n",
    "- 像日志"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 二、这些 memory 都是跨 thread 吗？\n",
    "\n",
    "> **是的（重点）。** ✅\n",
    "\n",
    "### ❌ 不是 state\n",
    "\n",
    "你之前学的 `MessagesState`、`checkpoint`、`thread` 这些是：**只属于当前 thread**\n",
    "\n",
    "### ✅ Memory Store 是全局的\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "Thread A\n",
    "Thread B   →→→  Memory Store\n",
    "Thread C\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "也就是说：\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "thread1: \"I like pizza\" → save_memory\n",
    "thread2: \"What do I like?\" → search_memory → pizza\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 **这节课所有 memory 都是跨 thread 的。**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 三、这些 memory 存在哪里？RAM 还是硬盘？\n",
    "\n",
    "> 这节课其实用了"教学版 storage"，不是 production storage。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1️⃣ 课程里的实现（默认）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from langgraph.store.memory import InMemoryStore\n",
    "\n",
    "# 存在 RAM 里\n",
    "# 速度快 ✅ | 简单 ✅\n",
    "# 程序一关就没了 ❌ | 不能持久化 ❌"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2️⃣ Production 应该用什么？\n",
    "\n",
    "| 方案 | 选项 |\n",
    "|------|------|\n",
    "| 数据库 | PostgreSQL / MongoDB / Redis |\n",
    "| 向量数据库（semantic memory） | Pinecone / Weaviate / Chroma |\n",
    "| 混合 | structured → SQL, semantic → vector DB |\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 **memory 是"逻辑概念"，不是绑定某种存储。**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3️⃣ 总结表格\n",
    "\n",
    "| 类型 | 是否跨 thread | 存哪里（课程） | 存哪里（生产） |\n",
    "|------|:---:|------|------|\n",
    "| State | ❌ | RAM | RAM |\n",
    "| Checkpoint | ❌ | RAM | DB |\n",
    "| Memory Store | ✅ | RAM (InMemoryStore) | DB / Vector DB |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 四、最容易混淆的点 ⚠️\n",
    "\n",
    "| ❌ 错误理解 | ✅ 正确理解 |\n",
    "|------|------|\n",
    "| memory = state | state = 当前对话上下文（短期）<br>memory = 长期知识库（跨对话） |\n",
    "| memory 自动发生 | LLM 必须决定：什么时候 save、什么时候 search |\n",
    "| memory 一定在硬盘 | memory 是逻辑层，存 RAM / DB / vector 都可以 |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 五、系统层面的理解 🏗️\n",
    "\n",
    "### 之前：\n",
    "```text\n",
    "Graph → 控制流程\n",
    "State → 当前上下文\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### 现在：\n",
    "```text\n",
    "Memory → 长期信息\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### 合起来：\n",
    "```text\n",
    "Agent = Graph + State + Memory\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 六、最后一句 💡\n",
    "\n",
    "> **这节课教你的不是"存一句话"，而是：如何让 agent 跨对话持续学习，并形成长期知识。**\n",
    "\n",
    "接下来要思考的关键问题：\n",
    "\n",
    "> **什么时候该写 memory？什么时候不该写？**\n",
    "\n",
    "这会直接决定你以后 agent 的质量。🎯"
   ]
  }
 ],
